          <from>MR. BAILLIE</from>
          <p>MR. BAILLIE : Mr. Speaker, I wish to draw the attention of members of the House to a number of distinguished visitors in the gallery opposite. First of all, Travis Price and his friend Megan Smith are with us today. Members may recognize Travis who, along with his friend David Shepherd, at Central Kings Rural High School started Pink Shirt Day, which has since spread across our country, in his efforts to combat bullying in our schools.</p>
        </speech>
        <speech by="#75109949-5b99-4b9c-b9fd-d85a8ce227ab">
