        <heading>COM. SRV. - TALBOT HOUSE: MIN. MISHANDLING - ADMIT</heading>
        <speech by="#6d07f2ae-9d4e-4ecf-8c75-26d9d9438690">
          <from>MS. KELLY REGAN</from>
          <p>MS. KELLY REGAN : Mr. Speaker, I am pleased to rise in my place this evening to speak on the issue of Talbot House. We've seen this issue unfold over the past several weeks. A couple of weeks ago in the House I did ask the minister what had gone on there and she assured us that it was the board's decision to close Talbot House.</p>
        </speech>
        <speech by="#75109949-5b99-4b9c-b9fd-d85a8ce227ab">
          <from>MR. SPEAKER</from>
          <p>MR. SPEAKER : The honourable Minister of Community Services.</p>
